  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink252-kilavi">varaiviṭai vaittup pirinta talaimakaṉ kuṟitta paruvattiṟku muṉṉē vantāṉāka vuvanta tōḻi talaimakaṭkuc colliyatu.  </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">
          What the confidante, who rejoiced as the hero—who had separated after he had placed a gap in [their] marriage—came before the appointed season, told the heroine.
          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink252">
<l>kuṉṟak kuṟavaṉ pulvēy kurampai</l>
<l>maṉṟā ṭiḷamaḻai maṟaikku nāṭaṉ</l>
<l>puraiyōṉ vāḻi tōḻi viraipeya</l>
<l>larumpaṉi yaḷaiiya kūtirp</l>
<l>peruntaṇ vāṭaiyiṉ muntuvan taṉaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>The man from the land where the young clouds</l>
        <l>that dance in the village common,</l>
        <l>conceal the grass-covered huts</l>
        <l>of the hill-dwellers on the hills—the great one—</l>
        <l rend="space indent3">O friend,</l> 
        <l>came before</l>
        <l>the great, cool northern winds</l>
        <l>of the cold season,</l>
        <l>in which swift showers mingle with difficult dew.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
